    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This exceptional vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation, presenting in true showroom condition. Every detail, from the flawless depth of its exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, reflects a standard of care that is rarely encountered. Meticulously maintained and mechanically superb, this unit offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or driver who demands uncompromising quality and investment-grade value. Experience the standard of excellence you deserve.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
